data.name: Counter Gem
data.desc: Send all cards in your Spell & Trap Card Zone to the Graveyard. Place as many "Crystal Beast" monsters as possible from your Graveyard in your Spell & Trap Card Zone, face-up, as Continuous Spell Cards. During the End Phase, destroy all face-up "Crystal Beast" cards you control.

card_sets.set_name: Structure Deck: Legend of the Crystal Beasts
